JavaScript User Authentication Libraries:

https://blog.bitsrc.io/6-javascript-user-authentication-libraries-for-2019-6c7c45fbe458  
//list of the most popular

I) Firebase Authentication //for small apps
- https://firebase.google.com/docs/auth/

II) Passport JS
- http://www.passportjs.org/docs/
- https://blog.risingstack.com/node-hero-node-js-authentication-passport-js/
- https://medium.freecodecamp.org/learn-how-to-handle-authentication-with-node-using-passport-js-4a56ed18e81e

III) Auth0
- https://auth0.com/docs/quickstart/webapp/nodejs
- https://auth0.com/docs/api/authentication#social

IV) PERMIT
- https://github.com/ianstormtaylor/permit
- https://github.com/ianstormtaylor/permit/tree/master/examples

V) GRANT
- https://github.com/jaredhanson/oauth2orize

VI) Feathers authentication management
- https://blog.feathersjs.com/how-to-setup-email-verification-in-feathersjs-72ce9882e744
- https://github.com/codingfriend1/Feathers-Vue

